race.comment: MY CUJO (3) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing eighth (20.38) in a Grade 6 at Q Lakeside. The form out of his last race has been franked. Tough to beat if on-song. MISS MOMENTUM (4) stuck on well last time to finish a neck back in second (16.74) at this track in a Grade 6 over 300m. Overdue and gets her chance. REVA TWIST (2) turned spotting a big start finishing sixth (20.76) last time in a Grade 6 at Q Lakeside. Warrants plenty of respect. ZABDON NO DOUBT (1) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at her latest outing at this circuit.
